summary: This is a Department of Justice Office of the Inspector General Investigations Division transcription request form for an interview recording from August 5, 2021. The form provides administrative details about the request, including case number, recording length, estimated cost, and approval information.

events.title: Interview Recording
events.description: An interview was conducted and recorded, with the recording being submitted for transcription. The recording length was 1 hour, 45 minutes, and 27 seconds.

keyFacts: The document is a DOJ OIG Investigations Division transcription request form for an interview recording.
The recording is from August 5, 2021, and is 1 hour, 45 minutes, and 27 seconds long.
The estimated transcription cost was $455.17, with an actual cost of $375.70.
The form includes administrative approval fields for supervisor and INV/HQ/ASB approval.
